long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Temporary Bookmarks allows you to save web pages for a set number of days, making it easy to organize and manage short-term bookmarks. You can view and manage all your temporary bookmarks in a convenient list, extend the time if needed, or remove them manually. Once the set time expires, bookmarks are automatically cleared, helping you keep your browsing clean and organized!
